detaileddescription.para: DataStatisticsCoordinator receives DataStatisticsEvent from {} every subtask and then merge them together. Once aggregation for all subtasks data statistics completes, DataStatisticsCoordinator will send the aggregated data statistics back to DataStatisticsOperator}. In the end a custom partitioner will distribute traffic based on the aggregated data statistics to improve data clustering. DataStatisticsCoordinator receives StatisticsEvent} from DataStatisticsOperator} every subtask and then merge them together. Once aggregation for all subtasks data statistics completes, DataStatisticsCoordinator will send the aggregated data statistics back to { DataStatisticsOperator}. In the end a custom partitioner will distribute traffic based on the aggregated data statistics to improve data clustering.
